cross: Paphiopedilum Blushing Petula x Paphiopedilum President Fred

measurements.description: One flat flower on a 23-cm inflorescence; dorsal sepal flat and wide, white veined green, blushed pink, darker distally; synsepal white veined green; petals slightly reflexed top edge, light green veined darker green, blushed pink-brown distal edges, a few distinct dark pink dots along hirsuite top edges; pouch light green, overlaid mahogany, darker veins; staminode green, darker markings; substance medium; texture glossy.
